#### S#9 (16s~18s)
**Visual Description:** 패딩의 전면부가 클로즈업되며, 지퍼, 포켓 등 기능적인 디테일이 세련된 디자인과 조화롭게 어우러진 모습을 보여준다.
```json
{
 "prompt": "A sleek, matte black insulated puffer jacket, modern and lightweight., A luxuriously soft, subtly textured urban setting, warm diffused light., Close-up on the jacket's functional details (zipper, pockets), showcasing the precise craftsmanship and stylish integration. Rembrandt lighting, Phase One IQ4, 8k, hyper-realistic --no text, logo",
 "styling": { "style": "craftsmanship, detail", "color": "monochromatic, crisp", "lighting": "accent, directional" }
}
```
