{
 "prompt": "A sleek, matte black insulated puffer jacket, modern and lightweight., A futuristic, minimalist architectural space, clean lines, high contrast., A stylish Asian man in his late 20s, with a modern haircut., Medium shot, man stands before a reflective glass wall, his image distorted/duplicated, highlighting the jacket's sharp lines. Hard/High Contrast lighting, Hasselblad X2D, 8k, hyper-realistic --no text, logo",
 "styling": { "style": "surreal, reflective", "color": "cool blue, stark white", "lighting": "specular, crisp" }
